step.datasource: SELECT TOP (1) 0 as DoQuit FROM dbo._AB_tb_ABEI_FileFolder_List l WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE 1=1 AND l.runid = '%runid%' AND l.isFolder = 0
SELECT l.ID, l.fullname, l.name FROM dbo._AB_tb_ABEI_FileFolder_List l WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE 1=1 AND l.runid = '%runid%' AND l.jobid = %jobid% AND l.isFolder = 0
SELECT l.ID, l.fullname, l.name FROM [%abeitargetdb%].dbo._AB_tb_ABEI_FileFolder_List l WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE 1=1 AND l.runid = '%runid%' AND l.jobid = %jobid% AND l.isFolder = 0

UPDATE l WITH (ROWLOCK, NOWAIT) SET rowstatus = CASE WHEN ISNULL(r.rowstatus ,-1) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE -1 END , sysmessage = r.errormessage , sysmodified = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP FROM dbo._AB_tb_ABEI_FileFolder_List l LEFT JOIN [%abeidb%].dbo._AB_Entity_results r with (nolock) ON r.runid = l.runid and r.jobid = %jobid% and r.ExactProduct = 'File' and r.Action = 'read' and r.ReferenceValue = CAST(l.ID as varchar(100)) WHERE 1=1 AND l.runid = '%runid%' AND l.jobid = %jobid% AND l.isFolder = 0

UPDATE r WITH (ROWLOCK, NOWAIT) SET abei_receiptdate = GETDATE() , abei_itemcode = g.artcode , abei_serial = g.facode , abei_stock = totalstock , seqno = %seqno% , rowstatus = CASE WHEN g.artcode is null or ISNULL(g.TotalStock,0) < r.orderline_unitamount THEN -1 ELSE 1 END , sysmessage = CASE WHEN g.artcode is null then 'Stock not found' WHEN ISNULL(g.TotalStock,0) < r.orderline_unitamount THEN 'Not enough stock available' ELSE r.sysmessage END , sysmodified = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP FROM [ABSC_Data].[dbo].[_AB_tb_VanReenen_WarehouseReceipt] r LEFT JOIN [400].dbo.items i with (NOLOCK) on i.itemcode = r.orderline_article_id collate database_default LEFT JOIN ( SELECT g.artcode, g.facode, g.warehouse, SUM(g.aantal) as TotalStock FROM [%abeisourcedb%]..gbkmut g with (NOLOCK) WHERE dagbknr = ' 70 ' and transtype = 'N' AND g.reknr = ' 3300' and g.warehouse = '32' GROUP BY g.artcode, g.facode, g.warehouse ) g ON g.artcode = r.orderline_article_id collate database_default and ( (i.isserialnumberitem = 0) OR ( i.isserialnumberitem = 1 and isnull(r.orderline_lot, '') collate database_default = isnull(g.facode,'' ) )) WHERE r.runid = '%runid%' AND r.rowstatus = 0

select distinct abei_itemcode as artcode, '30' as magcode FROM [ABSC_Data].[dbo].[_AB_tb_VanReenen_WarehouseReceipt] r where runid = '%runid%' and rowstatus = 1 AND not exists (select 1 from [%abeitargetdb%].dbo.voorrd vrd with (nolock) where vrd.magcode = '30' and vrd.artcode = abei_itemcode collate database_default)

select order_reference as HeaderID ,'A' as TransSubType ,'B' as Regelcode ,'151' as TransactionType ,GETDATE() As 'Datum' ,i.GLAccountDistribution as Reknr ,'VRT ' + order_reference As oms25 ,'600' as kstplcode ,itemcode AS artcode ,abei_serial AS facode ,'30' As warehouse ,ISNULL(orderline_unitamount,1) as aantal ,cast(ISNULL(orderline_unitamount,1) * i.CostPriceStandard as numeric (18,3)) as bdr_hfl ,GETDATE() As 'docdate' from [ABSC_Data].[dbo].[_AB_tb_VanReenen_WarehouseReceipt] r with (nolock) inner join [%abeitargetdb%].dbo.items i with (NOLOCK) on r.abei_itemcode = i.itemcode collate database_default where runid = '%runid%' and rowstatus = 1

select order_reference as HeaderID ,'B' as TransSubType ,'B' as Regelcode ,'150' as TransactionType ,GETDATE() As 'Datum' ,i.GLAccountDistribution as Reknr ,'VRT ' + order_reference As oms25 ,'600' as kstplcode ,itemcode AS artcode ,abei_serial AS facode ,'32' As warehouse ,-ISNULL(orderline_unitamount,1) as aantal ,cast(-ISNULL(orderline_unitamount,1) * i.CostPriceStandard as numeric (18,3)) as bdr_hfl ,GETDATE() As 'docdate' from [ABSC_Data].[dbo].[_AB_tb_VanReenen_WarehouseReceipt] r with (nolock) inner join [%abeitargetdb%].dbo.items i with (NOLOCK) on r.abei_itemcode = i.itemcode collate database_default where runid = '%runid%' and rowstatus = 1
select DISTINCT order_reference as HeaderID , 70 as dagbknr from [ABSC_Data].[dbo].[_AB_tb_VanReenen_WarehouseReceipt] with (nolock) where runid = '%runid%' and rowstatus = 1

UPDATE t WITH (ROWLOCK, NOWAIT) SET rowstatus = CASE WHEN ISNULL(r.rowstatus ,-1) = 2 THEN 2 ELSE -1 END , sysmessage = ISNULL(r.errormessage, 'No result found') , sysmodified = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP , seqno = %seqno% FROM dbo._AB_tb_VanReenen_WarehouseReceipt t LEFT JOIN [%abeidb%].dbo._AB_Entity_results r with (nolock) ON r.runid = t.runid and r.jobid = %jobid% and r.jobstepid = 3524 and r.HeaderID = t.order_reference WHERE 1=1 AND t.runid = '%runid%' AND t.rowstatus = 1

UPDATE l WITH (ROWLOCK, NOWAIT) SET rowstatus = CASE WHEN ISNULL(r.rowstatus, -1) = 2 THEN 2 ELSE -1 END , sysmessage = CASE WHEN ISNULL(r.rowstatus,-1) = 2 THEN 'Success' ELSE 'Error, check WarehouseReceipt table for details' END , sysmodified = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP FROM dbo._AB_tb_ABEI_FileFolder_List l OUTER APPLY ( SELECT MIN(w.rowstatus) as rowstatus FROM dbo._AB_tb_VanReenen_Warehousereceipt w WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE 1=1 AND w.runid = l.runid AND w.FileFolderListID = l.ID ) r WHERE 1=1 AND l.runid = '%runid%' AND l.jobid = %jobid% AND l.isFolder = 0 AND l.rowstatus = 1
SELECT l.ID, l.name FROM dbo._AB_tb_ABEI_FileFolder_List l WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE 1=1 AND l.runid = '%runid%' AND l.jobid = %jobid% AND l.isFolder = 0 AND l.rowstatus = 2
SELECT l.ID, l.name FROM dbo._AB_tb_ABEI_FileFolder_List l WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE 1=1 AND l.runid = '%runid%' AND l.jobid = %jobid% AND l.isFolder = 0 AND l.rowstatus <> 2
